<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM4.5.3">
<l>cōrvi ṉālporuḷ vaittatuṇ ṭākil</l>
<l rend="indent">collu colleṉṟu cuṟṟumi runtu</l>
<l>ārvi ṉavilum vāytiṟa vātē</l>
<l rend="indent">yantakālama ṭaivataṉ muṉṉam</l>
<l>mārva meṉpatōr kōyila maittu</l>
<l rend="indent">māta vaṉeṉṉun teyvattai naṭṭi</l>
<l>yārva meṉpatōr pūviṭa vallārk</l>
<l rend="indent">karava taṇṭatti luyyalu māmē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Before reaching the time [of death],</l>
<l rend="indent">if they question [you] on all sides,</l>
<l rend="indent">saying “If [you have] hoarded stolen wealth,</l>
<l rend="indent">tell [us]! Tell [us]!”,</l>
<l>without even opening [your] mouth,</l>
<l rend="indent">building a temple in [your] heart,</l>
<l>establish the god called Mādhava [there].</l>
<l>For those who are able to give the flower called love,</l>
<l rend="indent">there is escape from the punishment of Yama.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
